  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libxmlb</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libxmlb</application> package contains a library and a tool
which help create and query binary XML blobs.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
